å®šä¹‰ä¸€ä¸‹ perspective-box çš„æ ·å¼ï¼šå› ä¸ºå­å…ƒç´ æ˜¯ç»å¯¹å®šä½ï¼Œæ‰€ä»¥çˆ¶å…ƒç´ éœ€è¦ç›¸å¯¹å®šä½ï¼›ä¸ºäº†å®ç°ä¿¯è§†çš„ 3d æ•ˆæœï¼Œæˆ‘ä»¬å¯¹ perspective-origin è®¾ç½®äº† center topï¼Œå³ä¸­+ä¸Šã€‚

```CSS
.perspective-box {
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #26457a;
    position: relative;
    perspective: 1000px;
    perspective-origin: center top;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    user-select: none;
}
```

## æ´¾è’™ ğŸ‘¶

é¦–å…ˆå†™ä¸€ä¸‹ paimon çš„æ ·å¼ã€‚å°†ç›’å­å±…ä¸­ï¼Œå†ç”¨ drop-shadow åŠ ç‚¹å‘å…‰çš„ç‰¹æ•ˆ âœ¨

```CSS
:root {
    --glow-norm: drop-shadow(0 0 5px rgba(255, 255, 200, 0.8));
    --glow-intense: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 200, 0.8));
}

.paimon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 397px;
    height: 465px;
    animation: 3s infinite linear paimon-glow;
}

@keyframes paimon-glow {
    0% {
        -webkit-filter: var(--glow-norm);
        filter: var(--glow-norm);
    }

    50% {
        -webkit-filter: var(--glow-intense);
        filter: var(--glow-intense);
    }

    100% {
        -webkit-filter: var(--glow-norm);
        filter: var(--glow-norm);
    }
}
```

